## Reference
# https://www.robustperception.io/monitoring-kafka-with-prometheus

# Kafka Manager
1) open JMX port of kafka
2) download and configure kafka manager from github
3) easy to install and configure but ugly

# Grafana + Prometheus
key - getting metrics from java application
1) download JMX exporter and the kafka config file for prometheus
2) restart kafka with JMX reporter running as a java agent
3) setup Prometheus server
4) load the kafka overview dashboard from grafana.net into your Grafana to the console.  

